review_blob: I LOVED this beer! I want it here. I am a fan of Bass and Guiness and such and found myself choosing the Belikin Stout over Guiness when available. I dont know how to describe it other than it is great!
This was pretty good. Once back to Belize City it was all I could find. Id drink this one again, but would still chooses the Stout.
This beer may have been better if I had tried it before the Belikin Stout. This beer was described to me as a "womens beer". I was rather light and kind of boring. I had only one.
I tried Belikin when I first arrived in Belize. In Dangringa I still had not heard of the stout. I found Belikin to be rather refreshing and tasty. Just not something I would search out, but good.
